info.description:
==============
Cute Aurum CLI
==============

Commands::

    Usage:
      aurum-cli.py create account <username>
      aurum-cli.py create exercise <username> <ssh_url>
      aurum-cli.py package <path> <id> <key> <max_score> <min_score>
      aurum-cli.py quickmode <scorm_dir> [--new-user=<username>] [--zip]
      aurum-cli.py -h | --help
      aurum-cli.py --version


You can read the documentation `here <http://aurum-cli.readthedocs.org/en/latest/>`_ on readthedocs.org.
